title: Stainless Steel Appliances, BBQ/Picnic Area, Lush Landscaping
posting_body: The Becket Apartments was designed with the renter in mind.
Come visit our pet-friendly picturesque community with lush landscaping and amazing amenities.
Featuring a brand new resident lounge complete with an indoor swimming pool that opens to ample outdoor dining spaces with barbecue grills perfect for relaxing with family and friends.
Our state of the art fitness center is open 24 hours a day and provides a challenging workout for any level of exercise enthusiast.
Conveniently located within minutes to Renton's Boeing Campus and Renton Landing restaurants and shopping.
Our easy I-405 and I 5 access make for a quick commute to Downtown Seattle and the entire Eastside.
The Becket Apartments are a great place to call home!
Call and schedule a tour today!
